text: Petter Bjørheim (born 2 January 1965 in Stavanger) is a Norwegian politician for the Progress Party. He was elected to the Norwegian Parliament from Rogaland in 1989, but was not re-elected in 1993. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Progress Party (Norway) politicians Category:Members of the Storting Category:20th-century Norwegian politicians
